snippet: Chelsea stumbled into the semifinals of the Europa League despite losing to Rubin Kazan, and Basel also advanced by beating Tottenham in a penalty shootout.
abstract: Chelsea stumbles into Europa League semifinals despite 3-2 loss to FC Rubin Kazan.
